cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with image segmentation using neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a deep architecture based on residual learning suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of a convolutional Long Short Term Memory (LSTM) implies a focus on neural networks and deep learning (cs.NE). Finally, the datasets used in the experiments are related to medical imaging (cs.MM).
